Legendary F1 driver “Kaiser” Michael Schumacher in this old shot from 2012 spotted wearing the unusual Audemars Piguet Royal Oak Offshore Chronograph aka "Bumble Bee" ref 26176FO. 
It features a 42mm carbon case with fixed ceramic bezel, black and yellow dial with silver-tone hands and Arabic hour markers with date indication at 3 o'clock with sub-dials showing 60-second, 30-minute and 12-hour markers and a scratch-resistant crystal sapphire.
⌚️tag price: $35,000.00 (market price)
•
📸 @vertigo1983
